<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Invoice</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <img src="http://localhost:3000/public/assets/images/avatar.png" width="150" height="150" alt="logo" />

    <div class='text-3xl font-bold underline text-red-500'>Hello world!</div>
    You can use any tailwindcss library classes to style your invoice !
    <br />
    <br />
    {{#if name}}
      Here is the name you provided:
      {{name}}
    {{/if}}
    <br />
    <br />
    Format currency demo:
    {{formatCurrency 1000}}
    <br />
    <br />
    Format date demo:
    {{formatDate '2025-09-14'}}
  </body>
</html>